"title": "5547: speech, power and significance of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5547: speech, power and significance of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A person's speech has an enormous influence for good or ill and is a sure guide to character.</p>\n<h2>The impact of speech</h2>\n<h3>It has the power of life and death</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:21\">PRO 18:21</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:1-Jas3:12\">JAS 3:1–3:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:2\">PRO 15:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:4\">PRO 15:4</a></p>\n<h3>It can bring ruin or joy to the speaker</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:13-Prov12:14\">PRO 12:13–12:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps140:9\">PSA 140:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:14\">PRO 10:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:3\">PRO 13:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:3\">PRO 14:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:6-Prov18:7\">PRO 18:6–18:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:20\">PRO 18:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:23\">PRO 21:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl10:12-Eccl10:14\">ECC 10:12–10:14</a></p>\n<h3>It can destroy others</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:9\">PRO 11:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:2\">JOB 19:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps55:20-Ps55:21\">PSA 55:20–55:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps57:4\">PSA 57:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps64:3-Ps64:4\">PSA 64:3–64:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps140:3\">PSA 140:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:11\">PRO 11:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:6\">PRO 12:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:18\">PRO 12:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:27\">PRO 16:27</a></p>\n<h3>It can bring life to others</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:11\">PRO 10:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:20-Prov10:21\">PRO 10:20–10:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:31-Prov10:32\">PRO 10:31–10:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:21\">PRO 16:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:23-Prov16:24\">PRO 16:23–16:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov25:12\">PRO 25:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa50:4\">ISA 50:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:29\">EPH 4:29</a></p>\n<h2>The timing of speech</h2>\n<h3>There is an appropriate time for speaking</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl3:1-Eccl3:8\">ECC 3:1–3:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:23\">PRO 15:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:28\">PRO 15:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov25:11-Prov25:12\">PRO 25:11–25:12</a></p>\n<h3>There is an appropriate time for silence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:12-Prov11:13\">PRO 11:12–11:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam10:27\">1SA 10:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:19\">PRO 10:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:27-Prov17:28\">PRO 17:27–17:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:23\">PRO 21:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov26:4\">PRO 26:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:2-Eccl5:3\">ECC 5:2–5:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:13\">AMO 5:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:20\">HAB 2:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph1:7\">ZEP 1:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:19\">JAS 1:19</a></p>\n<h2>Spoken witness produces faith</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:17\">ROM 10:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa50:4\">ISA 50:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:40-Acts2:41\">ACT 2:40–2:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts28:23-Acts28:24\">ACT 28:23–28:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:15\">1PE 3:15</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ was silent before his accusers</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:22-1Pet2:23\">1PE 2:22–2:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:63\">MAT 26:63</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:61\">MRK 14:61</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:14\">MAT 27:14</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:5\">MRK 15:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:9\">LUK 23:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:8-John19:9\">JHN 19:8–19:9</a></p>\n<h2>Speech is an expression of a person's character</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:34-Matt12:37\">MAT 12:34–12:37</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps5:9\">PSA 5:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps15:1-Ps15:5\">PSA 15:1–15:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:10-Matt15:20\">MAT 15:10–15:20</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:14-Mark7:23\">MRK 7:14–7:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:45\">LUK 6:45</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:26\">JAS 1:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:5\">REV 14:5</a></p>",
